channel.description:
[center][size=15pt]Allstar The VeloCity 24-7[/size][/center]
My IGN is VeloCity and I'm creating currently an Allstar server. I used to make allstar server before, but my parents didn't let me run 24-7 server, because it was their computer. Since I live on my own now, I though let's try to make an Allstar server agian and get some players to might be interested to play agian and RUN 24-7 online. I got a new computer, so the server should be lagg not at all.
Download & upload speed: [img]http://www.speedtest.net/result/3638219155.png[/img]
I'm sorry that I can't currently give you any client, as you know I've got a new computer, so I have to make a new one.
I hope that you might interested and have fun!
Your Server Commander,
VeloCity(killer4577)
server status page at: [url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=82.75.204.241] click me.[/url]
